  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/48c60884cecddc0cd5fec36824101158.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.poster.avif?t=1761998071\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.webm?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.mp4?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In another timeline, Stratogun would have been the cabinet eating your pocket change at the local arcade. This is a modern revival of the classic 1980s space shooters, fast, unforgiving, and impossible to put down. Shoot, dodge, and outmaneuver swarms of enemies as you chase higher scores and unlock new ships, weapons, and perks. The question isn’t whether you’ll die, but how long you can last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/2f305b189fb031b01e048033e0be8bc0.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep inside, Stratogun is a lightning-fast space shooter where precision is survival. Every run turns chaos into progress as your score fuels new ships, weapons, and perks. The Red Orbit never lets up, and when the screen fills with fire and noise, only instinct keeps you alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20d6f4d7db7009a0185cda03e88b7171.poster.avif?t=1761998071\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20d6f4d7db7009a0185cda03e88b7171.webm?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20d6f4d7db7009a0185cda03e88b7171.mp4?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wireframe-inspired visuals meet explosive effects and a pounding synth soundtrack, bringing back the heart of the arcade with a modern edge. If you ever wished arcades still existed, this is your ticket back, no quarters required.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/20f6e4fd1070a8d9b4a37ef448472b14.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncompromised arcade gameplay and difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression system with unlockable ships, weapons, and perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wireframe-inspired neon visuals and synthwave soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global leaderboards </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/48c60884cecddc0cd5fec36824101158.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.poster.avif?t=1761998071\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.webm?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/58d27da72a482a44768bc046626a7933.mp4?t=1761998071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In another timeline, Stratogun would have been the cabinet eating your pocket change at the local arcade. This is a modern revival of the classic 1980s space shooters, fast, unforgiving, and impossible to put down. Shoot, dodge, and outmaneuver swarms of enemies as you chase higher scores and unlock new ships, weapons, and perks. The question isn’t whether you’ll die, but how long you can last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088430/extras/2f305b189fb031b01e048033e0be8bc0.avif?t=1761998071\" width=618 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep inside, Stratogun is a lightning-fast space shooter where precision is survival. Every run turns chaos into progress as your score fuels new ships, weapons, and perks. The Red Orbit never lets up, and when the screen fills with fire and noise, only instinct keeps you alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >